{
  "body": "## The problem\r\n\r\nThe [`bless`](https://docs.perl6.org/routine/bless) does not clarify that `bless` calls the superclass constructor. It also says:\r\n\r\n> (Though each time you write a custom constructor, remember that it makes subclassing harder).\r\n\r\nWhich is not exactly clear what it means. Why is it harder?\r\n\r\n## Suggestion\r\n\r\nAdd example of calling the superclass constructor and change or clarify that sentence. ",
